      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six engine. This high-revving power plant delivers 333 hp with exceptional throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise shift gates, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery out of corners. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics with updated bushings for a communicative steering feel. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a driver-focused vehicle, the drivetrain is dialed in and ready for the redline. This is a purist-spec example for those who value mechanical excellence and tactile engagement.",
      "price": 34500.0,
